div.div: This project is split into 3 components:

ol.li: Commons: Contracts and their basic implementation, all components and plugins will depend on it.
Parser: Implementation of the ANTLR4 parser. Will parse clausewitz script files into data that could be further processed.
Core: Consumes the data produced by the parser to create entries and values, find critical errors and convert entries to instances of other objects if a converter is provided.
